data.description: Meticulously maintained home in the Saint Andrews Commons neighborhood of Durham.  Homeowner has documentations and records for every improvement since the home was built. Hardwood floors, granite counter tops, center island with cooktop, private fenced-in back yard, open floor plan, whirlpool tub, and many other features. New roof in 2014 with 30 year warranty, and a new garage door this year. You must see this one inside and out!
